                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Accordion Item #3
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>This is the third item’s accordion body.</strong> It is hidden by default, until the collapse plugin adds the appropriate classes that we use to style each element. These classes control the overall appearance, as well as the showing and hiding via CSS transitions. You can modify any of this with custom CSS or overriding our default variables. It’s also worth noting that just about any HTML can go within the <code>.accordion-body</code>, though the transition does limit overflow.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="recent-reports">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-normal mb-3">Recent Reports & Requested Services</h1>
            <p class="mb-5 fs-5">View the most recent reports made by your community.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="reportcarousel" class="carousel slide carousel-dark">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div class="carousel-body">
                            <img src="~/images/FallenTree.jpg" />
                            <div class="container ms-2 mt-1 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                <h1>Fallen Tree on Main road</h1>
                                <p>Four trees were uprooted within 200m on Frans Conradie Drive in Bellville.</p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2"></i>
                                    Frans Conradie Drive, Bellville, Cape Town
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar me-2"></i>
                                    13 July 2020
                                </p>
                                <p class="align-self-end">
                                    <span class="badge text-black fs-5 fw-normal p-3 bg-warning">In Progress</span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="carousel-body">
                            <img src="~/images/StormFlood.jpg" />
                            <div class="container ms-2 mt-1 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                <h1>High School Destroyed by Strong Winds</h1>
                                <p>School structures at Nomzamo High School in Strand were severely damaged during a heavy Cape storm.</p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2"></i>
                                    Nomzamo High School, Strand, Cape Town
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar me-2"></i>
                                    13 July 2020
                                </p>
                                <p class="align-self-end">
                                    <span class="badge fs-5 fw-normal p-3 bg-success">Complete</span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="carousel-body">
                            <img src="~/images/Traffic.png" />
                            <div class="container ms-2 mt-1 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                <h1>N2 closed in Cape Town due to ongoing protest action</h1>
                                <p>Traffic congestion in Cape Town has intensified following ongoing protest actions that have led to significant disruptions on the N2 highway.</p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2"></i>
                                    N2 Highway, Cape Town
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar me-2"></i>
                                    22 May 2025
                                </p>
                                <p class="align-self-end">
                                    <span class="badge text-black fs-5 fw-normal p-3 bg-danger">On Going</span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#reportcarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#reportcarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-3">
        <div class="service-status">
            <p class="mb-3 fs-5">View the progress and current status of your requested services and reports!</p>
            <form asp-controller="Home" asp-action="ViewReports">
                <button class="btn btn-dark p-3 fs-5">
                    View all Reports
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="featured-services" id="services">
    <div class="container services-header">
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-normal border-bottom border-black border-2 pb-3">Featured Services</h1>
        <p class="text-opacity-75 fs-5 my-4">
            The featured services of this municipal application are designed to improve citizen engagement and streamline service delivery.
            The platform provides an efficient and user-friendly way for residents to report issues, track the status of their service requests,
            and access information on local events and announcements.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row my-5">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2 class="fs-3">Local Events and Announcements</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px;margin-top: 15px;">See what’s happening in your area and get the latest news from the municipality.</p>
                    <form class="ms-auto mt-auto" asp-controller="Post" asp-action="ViewPosts">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn fs-5 btn-primary">View</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2 class="fs-3">Request Municipal Services</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px;margin-top: 15px">Easily ask for municipal help for various needs, all in one place.</p>
                    <button class="btn disabled fs-5 btn-danger ms-auto mt-auto">Coming Soon</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2 class="fs-3">
                        Status of Service Requests
                    </h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px;margin-top: 15px;">Keep tabs on your requests and see their progress from start to finish. </p>
                    <button class="btn disabled fs-5 btn-danger ms-auto mt-auto">Coming Soon</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2 class="fs-3">Report Issues</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 15px;">Quickly report problems like potholes or power outages to the right municipal department.</p>
                    <form class="ms-auto mt-auto" asp-controller="Report" asp-action="CreateReport">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn fs-5 btn-warning">Report Now</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container mt-5 d-flex flex-row">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3310.7780657581266!2d18.428810200000004!3d-33.921111100000005!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1dcc5d89ebbfffff%3A0x607472ea9e6a0724!2sCape%20Town%20Civic%20Centre!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sza!4v1757440800391!5m2!1sen!2sza"
                width="900"
                height="650"
                style="border:2px solid black; border-radius: 10px;"
                allowfullscreen=""
